          "sketchCode": "\n// ⭐ Starfish Blinking LEDs\n// 6 Orange LEDs — 1 center + 5 arms\n// All blink together on pin 13\n//\n// Starfish Shape:\n//\n//         💡 Arm1 (Top)\n//        /         \\\n//  💡 Arm5        💡 Arm2\n//      |    💡     |\n//  💡 Arm4   CENTER  💡 Arm3\n//        \\         /\n//         (bottom)\n//\n// All 6 LEDs wired to pin 13 — they blink as one!\n\nconst int LED_PIN = 13;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(LED_PIN, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  // ⭐ Starfish GLOWS — all LEDs ON\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, HIGH);\n  delay(700);\n\n  // 🌑 Starfish SLEEPS — all LEDs OFF\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, LOW);\n  delay(300);\n}\n"
